headline: Top Dividend Stocks To Enhance Your Portfolio
summary: As the U.S. markets experience a strong start to the week, with major indices climbing over 1%, investors are keenly watching for corporate earnings and economic data that could influence Federal Reserve decisions on interest rates. In this environment of heightened market activity, dividend stocks remain an attractive option for those seeking steady income and potential growth, as they can offer stability amid broader market fluctuations.

headline: 2 REITs That Missed Out On The Rally
summary: Most REITs have risen a lot already, but some have missed this recovery and remain discounted. Check out two REIT stocks that remain opportunistic.
